Events.Text: Contact your ship's onboard computer (AI Assistant) and ask for help or explain the situation. (See instructions on the left panel.) [instruction 1 of 5]

Scenario.UserTask: Your spaceship is under attack! You must enter the combat deck to mount a counterattack. Unfortunately, you are locked out. Please work with the spaceship's onboard computer to unlock the door. You (Yoda) are the ship's Bartender. But you don't know the Access Code (yet).
Scenario.WizardTask: Act as the spaceship's onboard computer and help the user unlock the combat deck.
